widgets_values: {{In a large, transparent mushroom house, with light brown walls and a vaulted ceiling that reveals the blue sky, you can see a bear sleeping peacefully on a sofa shaped like a large tree leaf}}. {{The bear, with its brown fur and corpulent body, seems to be sound asleep, with its legs extended and its head resting on a fluffy pillow}}. {{The sofa, with its leaf shape and soft texture, invites comfort and relaxation, creating an atmosphere of peace and tranquility}}. {{The mushroom house, with its organic design and transparency, creates a sense of harmony with nature, while the sunlight, filtering through the walls, illuminates the scene with a warm and welcoming tone}}.
